data.description: Exquisite luxury living awaits you in this meticulously crafted one-story residence nestled in the prestigious community of Sun City. Boasting unparalleled elegance and unparalleled attention to detail, this stunning home offers a seamless blend of sophistication and comfort. As you enter through the grand foyer, be captivated by the soaring ceilings and an abundance of natural light that fills the expansive living spaces. The open floor plan effortlessly connects the gourmet kitchen, complete with top-of-the-line appliances and custom cabinetry, to the gracious dining area, Indulge in the lavish master suite, a true retreat featuring a spa-like ensuite bath with luxurious fixtures, a generously sized walk-in closet. Take a stroll out back to custom landscaped back yard with lush putting green perfect for events and get togethers. Don't forget the resort like community amenities, huge sparkling pool, work out area and much more! This home is a statement of opulence and refinement.
